  • Classes in org.uma.jmetal.problem.doubleproblem.impl used by org.uma.jmetal.problem.doubleproblem.impl 
    Class Description
    AbstractDoubleProblem
    Abstract class to be extended by implementations of interface {@link DoubleProblem>}, which must implement the Problem.evaluate(S) method.
    ComposableDoubleProblem
    This class allows to define a continuous (double) problem dynamically, by adding the ranges of every decision variable, the objective functions and the constraints.
